{"tid":562350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴：反車車長冇親身揸過大埔公路","createTime":"2018-02-15T22:00:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T09:15:54.000Z","uid":22054,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"927da9dd5055c3a935964f54f309696604a21899","tid":562350,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T22:00:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/521703/即時新聞/九巴承諾全面檢視車長培訓安排\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F521703%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4%E6%89%BF%E8%AB%BE%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E6%AA%A2%E8%A6%96%E8%BB%8A%E9%95%B7%E5%9F%B9%E8%A8%93%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92&d=XOKAt4ezNOtiMvOg3FSiiG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=8ec97667\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F521703%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4%E6%89%BF%E8%AB%BE%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E6%AA%A2%E8%A6%96%E8%BB%8A%E9%95%B7%E5%9F%B9%E8%A8%93%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92&h=7335eb01\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/521703/即時新聞/九巴承諾全面檢視車長培訓安排</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會交通事務委員會召開特別會議，討論大埔公路九巴意外，涉事車長有否接受正式路線訓練亦是關注焦點，<span style=\"color: red;\">九巴承認他駕駛出事路線前，沒有親自試駕，只是以「派紙仔」形式受訓，即坐在師傅旁邊觀察路段</span>，九巴承諾公司內部獨立調查，會全面檢視培訓安排。 <br />\n<br />\n一場車禍令公眾關注司機過往的定罪紀錄、駕駛態度及培訓問題，九巴向交通事務委員會提交資料，指二零一六年一共有二百三十六宗車長不小心駕駛記錄，去年就未能提供有多少宗。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一個焦點是涉事司機駕駛出事路線前，有否接受正式路線培訓，即有監督下自行試駕該條路線，抑或只是俗稱「派紙仔」，坐在師傅旁邊觀察路段，九巴指內部獨立調查時，會全面檢視車長培訓安排。<br />\n<br />\n/////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////<br />\n大公都未揸過就揸載人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712ddb078d47d1f3b3f19f81c7c6bf1601d25e80","tid":562350,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T22:36:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e786a8aef10ba6c9ef778c00eff192073d7e8982","tid":562350,"uid":95494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T01:27:52.000Z","msg":"又話佢唔係首次揸872？"},{"pid":"414bb014a22c9ad85da5997b3a8ee2c01e7afdcf","tid":562350,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e786a8aef10ba6c9ef778c00eff192073d7e8982","tid":562350,"uid":95494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T01:27:52.000Z","msg":"又話佢唔係首次揸872？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T01:29:08.000Z","msg":"高層渣乾渣淨員工"},{"pid":"94c33fd5fd85568a2afc4013855213f3db352f34","tid":562350,"uid":110832,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T02:27:15.000Z","msg":"關鳩事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最表面原因就廢老屌佢，佢唔順亂揸<br />\n最根本原因就係九巴垃圾制度冇正職返呢啲特別閪線"},{"pid":"607293f05b9e136dfdb454409472d5637ac339cd","tid":562350,"uid":41477,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T02:30:56.000Z","msg":"如果真係無行過條線,有機會打得甩"},{"pid":"13b82c34202cb2b06eca86adcae8f42be841a73e","tid":562350,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"607293f05b9e136dfdb454409472d5637ac339cd","tid":562350,"uid":41477,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T02:30:56.000Z","msg":"如果真係無行過條線,有機會打得甩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T03:31:40.000Z","msg":"點會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24d0530d77e69e79838369195bef98cf3c89bb2d","tid":562350,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"607293f05b9e136dfdb454409472d5637ac339cd","tid":562350,"uid":41477,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T02:30:56.000Z","msg":"如果真係無行過條線,有機會打得甩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T03:32:51.000Z","msg":"無渣過都知唔可以高速過彎啦   天才 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/